---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer — Books" description="What books.oriz.in is and isn't." hideSidebar={true}>
  <header class="container-prose page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">Books</a> / <a href="/legal/">Legal</a> / Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="container-prose prose">
    <p>
      Everything on books.oriz.in is published in good faith for general
      information only. Use it at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>NCERT is the source of truth</h2>
    <p>
      NCERT is the publisher and copyright holder of the textbooks indexed
      here. Books does not host the PDFs — every download button links
      directly to <code>ncert.nic.in</code>. If a download fails, the source
      file at NCERT is the one that's broken; reach out via the
      <a href="/contact/">contact form</a> and we'll either find an alternate
      link or remove the listing.
    </p>

    <h2>Not professional advice</h2>
    <p>
      Books indexes school curriculum material for browsing convenience.
      Nothing here constitutes academic, legal, medical, or career advice.
      Consult a qualified professional for those.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      Every textbook page links to <code>ncert.nic.in</code> or other official
      sources. We don't control their content or uptime, and inclusion is
      not an endorsement.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Books does not currently use affiliate links. If that ever changes, the
      links will be marked, and this page will be updated.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head { padding-block: 3rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .eyebrow { color: var(--color-fg-muted); font-size: 0.8125rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .eyebrow a { color: var(--color-fg-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }
  .meta { color: var(--color-fg-soft); font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0; }
  .prose { padding-block: 2.5rem 4rem; color: var(--color-prose); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.0625rem; }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .prose code { background: var(--color-bg-muted); padding: 0.125em 0.375em; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.875em; }
</style>
